  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bb2 \u0b87\u0b9a\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd..!",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Famous music composer died suddenly..!",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The sudden death of the famous music composer has shocked the Malayalam film industry and fans alike.",
        "52-year-old John B Vargi, a popular music composer, has captured the hearts of thousands of Malayalam fans with his music. His death due to sudden illness is shocking.",
        "He has composed music for some popular Malayalam films like Kammattipadam, Neithukaran, Penkodi, Unnam etc. released in Malayalam. Vargi, who was living in her house in Mullakara, Kerala state, is said to have fainted at her house due to a sudden decline in her health. Following this, he was admitted to the hospital and died due to treatment. His death has left the entire film industry and fans in mourning.",
        "Apart from composing music for Malayalam films and songs, Vargi has also worked in some Hindi, Kannada and Tamil films. He composed difficult songs for a Malayalam rock band named Avyal.",
        "He was a key member of the band Jigsaw Puzzle. In 2007, Vargi was adjudged Best Music Composer for the drama film Frozen at the Madrid Imagine India Film Festival.",
        "A guitarist, he studied guitar at London's Trinity College of Music. He rose to fame after releasing three albums with his band, Jigsaw Puzzle.",
        "Celebrities and fans are paying their tributes to him as the most talented music composer of Malayalam film industry, his loss is irreparable. Notably, Vargie has two children with his wife, Baby John, and Job and Joseph John."
      ],
